| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4361 — Recovery Inhibition (8base)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c0bae5c3-f24b-5dff-a9e2-e649fd4e7a25"
